net.peierls.expr

Interface DelegatingOperator

  • All Superinterfaces:
    BinaryOp, Operator, UnaryOp
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    BasicOperator, TrigonometricOperator

    public interface DelegatingOperator
extends UnaryOp, BinaryOp
    A partial implementation of both the unary and binary operator interfaces that delegates to an underlying operator.
